{"tid":1394750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於選民登記 ！重要！","createTime":"2019-08-01T13:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T03:35:45.000Z","uid":271334,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8127c67e5d8eb22c5ba7db24ce1772714ef4fa4d","tid":1394750,"uid":271334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:54:07.000Z","msg":"是咁的 , 有朋友做緊選舉事務處 <br />\n佢話臨尾時民賤聯都交左好多假FORM黎<br />\n而今日都有新聞都有報 有位先生 被登記左做另一區選民<br />\n所以我FD提大家請抽出少少時間<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<strong>8月25號前打去 選舉事務處熱線  2891 1001 <br />\n或官網有個查核系統 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/home.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voterregistration.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fhome.htm&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=e6b77a74\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/home.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n確認返自己 登記個地址是否正確  <br />\n同埋對埋選區同票站有無錯</strong></span><br />\n如果有嘢錯 記得25號前打去屌<br />\n唔該曬大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家小心唔好「被登記」另一區選民啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後咁就益撚左民賤聯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n( FD 話佢地成撚日比假FORM <br />\n但最弊上司落ORDER話照做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) <br />\n<br />\n希望大家抽少少時間睇下自己有無被登記錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d0fab3624b95faba3c28149fae81b0f37248ad","tid":1394750,"uid":125029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:55:48.000Z","msg":"同我瘋狂推爆「公務員事務局」FB Page<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1394653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1394653</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"574606460528c1dd11e9697fb4ca0ae76e9eb80d","tid":1394750,"uid":279810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r