plyTime":"2019-08-01T18:56:43.000Z","msg":"臨訓前<br />\n8.5 罷工"},{"pid":"e0f1b4e032d507bd695d722c5598d473305368ab","tid":1394750,"uid":139247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:11:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42cdbe2d3c9970dae178a22e7bd7c8b9cfd90974","tid":1394750,"uid":83989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:45:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fmob%2F&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=9013af89\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>2019年臨時選民登記冊已於2019年8月1日發表。<br />\n<br />\n你可以使用本網站搜尋資料以確定自己是否一名已登記選民，以及查閱你在上述選民登記冊上的現有登記資料。就編製下一份選民登記冊而言，如果你已提交登記申請或更新登記資料，而選舉事務處亦已成功處理有關申請，你亦可查閱你的最新登記資料。</em><br />\n<br />\n<strong>麻煩大家不嫌其煩重新check吓有無被dq,另外新登記人士麻煩check吓是否已成功登記<br />\n<br />\n<ins>2019年11月24日（星期日）區議會選舉</ins> <br />\n麻煩大家記得預留當日投票！踢走晒民建聯！</strong>"},{"pid":"e2e465c791d150575a81df60acd60399e0315b4f","tid":1394750,"uid":299161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:07:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92d3acbd9cc6716be6fe8238e24f1a9e8e5cce0b","tid":1394750,"uid":271334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:24:09.000Z","msg":"8月25 前<br />\n仲有半個月有多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a16d95e2a2e424595bc2ede6b3ab345740292f","tid":1394750,"uid":262193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:45:59.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e4380c585bdcd7816af308fb97619da19d0443","tid":1394750,"uid":271334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:08